---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="GP — FRACGP Examinations" description="RACGP FRACGP examination overview — AKT, KFP, and CCE.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>FRACGP Examinations</h1>
    <p>General Practice — RACGP · 3 components required for fellowship</p>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Three Examination Components</h2>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Applied Knowledge Test (AKT)</div>
      <p>Written exam testing applied knowledge across general practice clinical topics. MCQ-based.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Key Feature Problem (KFP)</div>
      <p>Written exam assessing clinical decision-making in complex GP scenarios. Tests identification and management of key features in patient cases.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Clinical Competency Exam (CCE)</div>
      <p>Structured clinical examination assessing competence in real or simulated GP consultations. Tests communication, clinical reasoning, and management.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Exam Support</h2>
    <p>The RACGP provides exam preparation resources through the training program. The <strong>Yagila Wadamba Exam Support Program</strong> offers additional support for Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander doctors.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
